DotDot Attributes Serializer
Unify Components » DotDot Serializer

This component provides helper functions for parsing the Attribute space of topics and generates Unify json payloads sent over MQTT. More...

Detailed Description

This component provides helper functions for parsing the Attribute space of topics and generates Unify json payloads sent over MQTT.

◆ uic_mqtt_dotdot_attribute_update_type_t

enum uic_mqtt_dotdot_attribute_update_type_t

Attribute value updated type.

Enumerator
UCL_DESIRED_UPDATED 

The Desired value of an attribute has been updated

UCL_REPORTED_UPDATED 

The Reported value of an attribute has been updated
